{
  "info": {
    "name": "SOLO API",
    "description": "Import this file in Postman: **Import** → **Upload Files** → choose `backend/postman/SOLO-auth.postman_collection.json`.\n\n**Setup — SOLO API:** Set **`baseUrl`**. **Auth (Supabase):** Set **`supabaseUrl`** (project URL, no trailing slash — same as **`SUPABASE_URL`** in **`.env`**) and **`supabaseAnonKey`** (**`SUPABASE_ANON_KEY`**). Set **`authEmail`** + **`authPassword`**. Run **Auth (Supabase) → Sign in** to fill **`accessToken`** (or **Sign up** first if the project returns a session; if email confirmation is enabled, confirm the user then **Sign in**).\n\n**Recommended API flow:** **Create idea** → **`ideaId`** saved → **AI → Send prompt** (optional; **`OPENAI_API_KEY`** on server) → **Storage → Upload files** (optional; R2 + **`CLOUDFLARE_R2_*`** on server) → **Create mindmap** → **`mindmapId`** saved → **Mindmap-nodes** / **Mindmap-connections** (both **require** that mind map id — query **`mindmap_id`** on **`GET`**, JSON **`mindmapId`** on **`POST`/`PATCH`**). **`nodeId`** / **`connectionId`** / **`objectiveId`** set on **`201`** via Tests scripts; **`GET /mindmaps/:id`** and **`DELETE /mindmaps/:id`** require query **`idea_id`** matching the map.\n\n**Swift / HTTP mapping**\n- **Ideas** → **`IdeaController`** / **`IdeasRemoteDataSource`**.\n- **Storage** → **`StorageRemoteDataSource`** — **`POST /storage/presigned-put`**, **`PUT`** to signed URL, **`POST /storage/files`**.\n- **Mindmaps** → **`POST/GET/DELETE /mindmaps`** (document load **`GET /mindmaps/:id?idea_id=`**).\n- **Mindmap-nodes** → **`MindmapNodeController`** — **`mindmap_id`** (**required**) on **`GET /mindmap-node?mindmap_id={{mindmapId}}`**; **`mindmapId`** (**required**) in create/update JSON.\n- **Mindmap-connections** → **`MindmapConnectionController`** — **`mindmap_id`** (**required**) on **`GET /mindmap-connection?mindmap_id={{mindmapId}}`**; **`mindmapId`** (**required**) in create/update JSON.\n- **Objectives** → **`ObjectiveController`** — create (**`POST /objectives`**) requires **`ideaId`** in JSON (camelCase).\n- **`AuthController`** (Swift) uses Supabase only for auth; this collection’s **Auth (Supabase)** folder calls **`{{supabaseUrl}}/auth/v1/...`** (not **`{{baseUrl}}`**).\n\nIf **Update idea** fails, check **`ideaId`** in Postman Console or try **PUT** instead of **PATCH**.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
