    {
      "name": "Auth (Supabase)",
      "description": "GoTrue (**`/auth/v1`**) — same service the Swift **`AuthController`** uses. Headers **`apikey`** + **`Authorization: Bearer …`** must be your anon key (**`SUPABASE_ANON_KEY`**).\n\n- **Sign in** — **`200`** with **`access_token`** → Tests set collection **`accessToken`** for **`{{baseUrl}}`** requests.\n- **Sign up** — matches app metadata shape **`first_name`** / **`last_name`**. If your project requires email confirmation, you may get a user without **`access_token`**; use **Sign in** after confirming.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Sign in (password)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "  const data = pm.response.json();",
                  "  const t = data && data.access_token;",
                  "  if (t) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', t);",
                  "  }",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "apikey",
                "value": "{{supabaseAnonKey}}",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{supabaseAnonKey}}",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "key": "Accept",
                "value": "application/json",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{authEmail}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{authPassword}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{supabaseUrl}}/auth/v1/token?grant_type=password",
              "host": ["{{supabaseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "v1", "token"],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "grant_type",
                  "value": "password"
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Maps to Supabase **`signInWithPassword`**. Requires **`supabaseUrl`**, **`supabaseAnonKey`**, **`authEmail`**, **`authPassword`**. Response **`access_token`** is copied to **`accessToken`**."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Sign up (email + password)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200 || pm.response.code === 201) {",
                  "  const data = pm.response.json();",
                  "  const t = data && data.access_token;",
                  "  if (t) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', t);",
                  "  }",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "apikey",
                "value": "{{supabaseAnonKey}}",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{supabaseAnonKey}}",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "key": "Accept",
                "value": "application/json",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{authEmail}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{authPassword}}\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"first_name\": \"{{authFirstName}}\",\n    \"last_name\": \"{{authLastName}}\"\n  }\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{supabaseUrl}}/auth/v1/signup",
              "host": ["{{supabaseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "v1", "signup"]
            },
            "description": "Maps to Swift **`signUp`** (**`first_name`** / **`last_name`** in **`data`**). When Supabase returns a session (**`access_token`** at the root), Tests set **`accessToken`**. Otherwise run **Sign in** after confirming email (if enabled)."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Ideas",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "List ideas (fetchIdeas)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{accessToken}}",
                "type": "text"
              },
              {
                "key": "Accept",
                "value": "application/json",
                "type": "text"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/ideas?sort=created_desc&q=",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["ideas"],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "sort",
                  "value": "created_desc",
                  "description": "title_asc | created_desc | created_asc | updated_desc"
                },
                {
                  "key": "q",
                  "value": "",
