            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/ideas/{{ideaId}}",
            "description": "Maps to **`IdeaController.togglePublished`** — calls **`editIdea`** with **`isPublished`** flipped. **`isPublished`** is camelCase (matches Swift **`EditIdeaRequestBody`**). Adjust **`title`/`purpose`** to match the idea or fetch first via **List ideas**."
